\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6571359\charrsid10367775  up after 'em you see. And - snagging turnips - in the field. When we're leaving corn, I used to drive the horses up - backwards and forwards you see, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5968924\charrsid10367775 leaving}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6571359\charrsid10367775  the corn up the - the - at the far end, with the sack you see. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16056826 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6571359\charrsid10367775 A nice healthy life?
