k in the morning 'til five at night. Yes. That's - through the day. And then - the horses we had to do after five o'clock and we used to go back at seven 'til eight. Oh yes, to bed 'em up and - and - and feed 'em for the night you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16056826 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6571359\charrsid10367775 Did you work on Sunday as well?
