Well - more or less - wintertime you see, the sheep was to feed you see. But summertime well there wasn't you see 'cos the - these sheep was running out in the fields you see. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16056826 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6571359\charrsid10367775 So you had more time off in summertime?
